Plus, I need to keep track of whether there’s a problem with coroutines and AssertJ compatibility. Also, headless AWT could introduce potential worries, but it's probably not an immediate concern.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Analyzing EDT behavior in tests**\\n\\nI'm considering whether tests could create an EDT that never stops, which might prevent normal JVM tests from exiting. The AWT EventDispatchThread is non-daemon, so I wonder if AWT threads could indeed prevent the application from exiting altogether. In a headless environment, though, it seems the EDT might terminate if there are no events for a certain timeout period. Overall, I need to think about how this could impact the behavior of my tests and application.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering the test file**\\n\\nI don't have a report, so I need to keep only the test file. I’m wondering if I can use `hintOnError`, but it seems like that won’t work. Maybe using `Dispatchers.Main` will lead to loading `SwingDispatcherFactory` and its `loadPriority/createDispatcher`. That's a good point! No internet is needed for this process, so I should focus on rewriting the file accordingly.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_N7ODbUukdPQIK0ETV4KoRgai|fc_086da29bb38939770169faac69b7108192b22a1fc78ee9b782", "name": "write", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/org.jetbrains.kotlinx/kotlinx-coroutines-swing/1.10.2/src/test/kotlin/org_jetbrains_kotlinx/kotlinx_coroutines_swing/Kotlinx_coroutines_swingTest.kt", "content": "/*\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\n *\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\n */\npackage org_jetbrains_kotlinx.kotlinx_coroutines_swing\n\nimport java.util.concurrent.atomic.AtomicBoolean\nimport javax.swing.SwingUtilities\nimport kotlin.coroutines.ContinuationInterceptor\nimport kotlin.coroutines.coroutineContext\nimport kotlinx.coroutines.Dispatchers\nimport kotlinx.coroutines.async\nimport kotlinx.coroutines.cancelAndJoin\nimport kotlinx.coroutines.delay\nimport kotlinx.coroutines.launch\nimport kotlinx.coroutines.runBlocking\nimport kotlinx.coroutines.swing.Swing\nimport kotlinx.coroutines.withContext\nimport kotlinx.coroutines.withTimeout\nimport org.assertj.core.api.Assertions.assertThat\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test\n\npublic class Kotlinx_coroutines_swingTest {\n    @Test\n    fun swingDispatcherRunsCoroutineBodyOnEventDispatchThread(): Unit = runBlocking {\n        withTimeout(5_000) {\n            val callerThread: Thread = Thread.currentThread()\n\n            val result: SwingThreadResult = withContext(Dispatchers.Swing) {\n                SwingThreadResult(\n                    isEventDispatchThread = SwingUtilities.isEventDispatchThread(),\n                    thread = Thread.currentThread(),\n                    dispatcher = coroutineContext[ContinuationInterceptor],\n                )\n            }\n\n            assertThat(result.isEventDispatchThread).isTrue()\n            assertThat(result.thread).isNotSameAs(callerThread)\n            assertThat(result.dispatcher).isSameAs(Dispatchers.Swing)\n        }\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    fun mainDispatcherIsProvidedBySwingFactoryAndDispatchesToEventDispatchThread(): Unit = runBlocking {\n        withTimeout(5_000) {\n            val result: SwingThreadResult = withContext(Dispatchers.Main) {\n                SwingThreadResult(\n                    isEventDispatchThread = SwingUtilities.isEventDispatchThread(),\n                    thread = Thread.currentThread(),\n                    dispatcher = coroutineContext[ContinuationInterceptor],\n                )\n            }\n\n            assertThat(result.isEventDispatchThread).isTrue()\n            assertThat(result.dispatcher).isSameAs(Dispatchers.Main)\n            assertThat(Dispatchers.Main.immediate).isSameAs(Dispatchers.Swing.immediate)\n        }\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    fun immediateDispatcherRunsInlineOnlyWhenAlreadyOnEventDispatchThread(): Unit = runBlocking {\n        withTimeout(5_000) {\n            assertThat(Dispatchers.Swing.immediate.isDispatchNeeded(coroutineContext)).isTrue()\n\n            val events: MutableList<String> = mutableListOf()\n            withContext(Dispatchers.Swing) {\n                val eventDispatchThread: Thread = Thread.currentThread()\n\n                assertThat(Dispatchers.Swing.isDispatchNeeded(coroutineContext)).isTrue()\n                assertThat(Dispatchers.Swing.immediate.isDispatchNeeded(coroutineContext)).isFalse()\n                assertThat(Dispatchers.Swing.immediate.immediate).isSameAs(Dispatchers.Swing.immediate)\n\n                withContext(Dispatchers.Swing.immediate) {\n                    events += \"immediate\"\n                    assertThat(Thread.currentThread()).isSameAs(eventDispatchThread)\n                    assertThat(SwingUtilities.isEventDispatchThread()).isTrue()\n                }\n                events += \"after-immediate\"\n            }\n\n            assertThat(events).containsExactly(\"immediate\", \"after-immediate\")\n        }\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    fun asyncWorkComposesOnSwingDispatcher(): Unit = runBlocking {\n        withTimeout(5_000) {\n            val combined: String = withContext(Dispatchers.Swing) {\n                val greeting = async(Dispatchers.Swing.immediate) {\n                    assertThat(SwingUtilities.isEventDispatchThread()).isTrue()\n                    \"hello\"\n                }\n                val target = async(Dispatchers.Swing.immediate) {\n                    assertThat(SwingUtilities.isEventDispatchThread()).isTrue()\n                    \"swing\"\n                }\n\n                \"${greeting.await()} ${target.await()}\"\n            }\n\n            assertThat(combined).isEqualTo(\"hello swing\")\n        }\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    fun delayResumesOnEventDispatchThreadAndCancellationStopsPendingContinuation(): Unit = runBlocking {\n        withTimeout(5_000) {\n            val events: MutableList<String> = mutableListOf()\n\n            withContext(Dispatchers.Swing) {\n                events += \"before-delay\"\n                delay(10)\n                assertThat(SwingUtilities.isEventDispatchThread()).isTrue()\n                events += \"after-delay\"\n            }\n\n            val completedAfterCancellation = AtomicBoolean(false)\n            val job = launch(Dispatchers.Swing) {\n                delay(10_000)\n                completedAfterCancellation.set(true)\n            }\n\n            job.cancelAndJoin()\n\n            assertThat(events).containsExactly(\"before-delay\", \"after-delay\")\n            assertThat(completedAfterCancellation).isFalse()\n        }\n    }\n}\n\nprivate data class SwingThreadResult(\n    val isEventDispatchThread: Boolean,\n    val thread: Thread,\n    val dispatcher: ContinuationInterceptor?,\n)\n"}, "partialJson": "{\"path\":\"tests/src/org.jetbrains.kotlinx/kotlinx-coroutines-swing/1.10.2/src/test/kotlin/org_jetbrains_kotlinx/kotlinx_coroutines_swing/Kotlinx_coroutines_swingTest.kt\",\"content\":\"/*\\n * Copyright and related rights waived via CC0\\n *\\n * You should have received a copy of the CC0 legalcode along with this\\n * work. If not, see <http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>.\\n */\\npackage org_jetbrains_kotlinx.kotlinx_coroutines_swing\\n\\nimport java.util.concurrent.atomic.AtomicBoolean\\nimport javax.swing.SwingUtilities\\nimport kotlin.coroutines.ContinuationInterceptor\\nimport kotlin.coroutines.coroutineContext\\nimport kotlinx.coroutines.Dispatchers\\nimport kotlinx.coroutines.async\\nimport kotlinx.coroutines.cancelAndJoin\\nimport kotlinx.coroutines.delay\\nimport kotlinx.coroutines.launch\\nimport kotlinx.coroutines.runBlocking\\nimport kotlinx.coroutines.swing.Swing\\nimport kotlinx.coroutines.withContext\\nimport kotlinx.coroutines.withTimeout\\nimport org.assertj.core.api.Assertions.assertThat\\nimport org.junit.jupiter.api.Test\\n\\npublic class Kotlinx_coroutines_swingTest {\\n    @Test\\n    fun swingDispatcherRunsCoroutineBodyOnEventDispatchThread(): Unit = runBlocking {\\n        withTimeout(5_000) {\\n            val callerThread: Thread = Thread.currentThread()\\n\\n            val result: SwingThreadResult = withContext(Dispatchers.Swing) {\\n                SwingThreadResult(\\n                    isEventDispatchThread = SwingUtilities.isEventDispatchThread(),\\n                    thread = Thread.currentThread(),\\n                    dispatcher = coroutineContext[ContinuationInterceptor],\\n                )\\n            }\\n\\n            assertThat(result.isEventDispatchThread).isTrue()\\n            assertThat(result.thread).isNotSameAs(callerThread)\\n            assertThat(result.dispatcher).isSameAs(Dispatchers.Swing)\\n        }\\n    }\\n\\n    @Test\\n    fun mainDispatcherIsProvidedBySwingFactoryAndDispatchesToEventDispatchThread(): Unit = runBlocking {\\n        withTimeout(5_000) {\\n            val result: SwingThreadResult = withContext(Dispatchers.Main) {\\n                SwingThreadResult(\\n                    isEventDispatchThread = SwingUtilities.isEventDispatchThread(),\\n                    thread = Thread.currentThread(),\\n                    dispatcher = coroutineContext[ContinuationInterceptor],\\n                )\\n            }\\n\\n            assertThat(result.isEventDispatchThread).isTrue()\\n            assertThat(result.dispatcher).isSameAs(Dispatchers.Main)\\n            assertThat(Dispatchers.Main.immediate).isSameAs(Dispatchers.Swing.immediate)\\n        }\\n    }\\n\\n    @Test\\n    fun immediateDispatcherRunsInlineOnlyWhenAlreadyOnEventDispatchThread(): Unit = runBlocking {\\n        withTimeout(5_000) {\\n            assertThat(Dispatchers.Swing.immediate.isDispatchNeeded(coroutineContext)).isTrue()\\n\\n            val events: MutableList<String> = mutableListOf()\\n            withContext(Dispatchers.Swing) {\\n                val eventDispatchThread: Thread = Thread.currentThread()\\n\\n                assertThat(Dispatchers.Swing.isDispatchNeeded(coroutineContext)).isTrue()\\n                assertThat(Dispatchers.Swing.immediate.isDispatchNeeded(coroutineContext)).isFalse()\\n                assertThat(Dispatchers.Swing.immediate.immediate).isSameAs(Dispatchers.Swing.immediate)\\n\\n                withContext(Dispatchers.Swing.immediate) {\\n                    events += \\\"immediate\\\"\\n                    assertThat(Thread.currentThread()).isSameAs(eventDispatchThread)\\n                    assertThat(SwingUtilities.isEventDispatchThread()).isTrue()\\n                }\\n                events += \\\"after-immediate\\\"\\n            }\\n\\n            assertThat(events).containsExactly(\\\"immediate\\\", \\\"after-immediate\\\")\\n        }\\n    }\\n\\n    @Test\\n    fun asyncWorkComposesOnSwingDispatcher(): Unit = runBlocking {\\n        withTimeout(5_000) {\\n            val combined: String = withContext(Dispatchers.Swing) {\\n                val greeting = async(Dispatchers.Swing.immediate) {\\n                    assertThat(SwingUtilities.isEventDispatchThread()).isTrue()\\n                    \\\"hello\\\"\\n                }\\n                val target = async(Dispatchers.Swing.immediate) {\\n                    assertThat(SwingUtilities.isEventDispatchThread()).isTrue()\\n                    \\\"swing\\\"\\n                }\\n\\n                \\\"${greeting.await()} ${target.await()}\\\"\\n            }\\n\\n            assertThat(combined).isEqualTo(\\\"hello swing\\\")\\n        }\\n    }\\n\\n    @Test\\n    fun delayResumesOnEventDispatchThreadAndCancellationStopsPendingContinuation(): Unit = runBlocking {\\n        withTimeout(5_000) {\\n            val events: MutableList<String> = mutableListOf()\\n\\n            withContext(Dispatchers.Swing) {\\n                events += \\\"before-delay\\\"\\n                delay(10)\\n             